comment:
Heard is not only an abuser, she's a manipulative liar. She has permanently negatively effected Depp's life and career. He not only is suffering from a besmirched public image, he's also a victim of abuse and that trauma will stay with him. What's worse than having your partner, someone you love, the person you trust most in life and whose betrayal would be the most devastating of all, abuse you? Having all that happen and then be told you're lying and be punished for being the victim while the abuser is rewarded for committing the abuse. Victims of abuse are often afraid to come forward, afraid of repercussions, of not being believed, of being told it was their own fault. With men abused by female partners, you add to that a major stigma. Women are not nearly as likely to commit abuse or violence, but to say it never happens is unrealistic. And for all the people saying Depp is bigger and stronger, how could *she* abuse *him* with her small frame? That's part of it! Depp knows he could win in a fight with her, and he knows if she punches him 10 times, and he slaps her in response, he's going to be able to do more damage and he is the one who's going to get in trouble. He *can't* realistically defend himself.¬†

Here's another point of what amount of damage she's done,
Every time a woman falsely accuses someone of domestic violence, 100 real victims are not believed. Now multiply that by her power, position, and status. Her voice telling these lies amplifies this negative effect insurmountably. She has done irreparable damage to all victims of domestic violence. In the US 1 in 4 women will be victims of *repeated* physical domestic violence, including beatings, burnings, and/or strangulation. 1 in 3 women will be physically abused by a male partner at some point in their lives. We will never really know how much damage her lies have caused, but she has not only ruined Depp's life, she's deeply harmed every actual victim of domestic violence who is or will be. Many victims who chose to come forward and report will not be believed, and accused of just trying to ruin someone's life for revenge. Many others will be too scared to come forward at all. 

Heard needs to be more than fired, she needs to be held responsible for her many crimes.
